OL,3,CWinter fuel payments cut could drive
OL,4,C100,000 pensioners into poverty
OL,6,FThe Government has published internal
OL,7,Fmodelling that shows it expects it's
OL,8,Fcontroversial policy to means test
OL,9,FWinter Fuel Payments will drive
OL,10,Fbetween 50 and 100,000 extra
OL,11,Fpensioners into poverty.
OL,13,FThe welfare secretary, Liz Kendall,
OL,14,Frevealed the figures in a letter to
OL,15,Fparliament's work and pensions
OL,16,Fcommittee.
OL,18,FConservatives immediately seized on
OL,19,Fthe admission.
