OL,3,CWinter fuel payments cut could drive
OL,4,C100,000 pensioners into poverty
OL,6,FShadow work and pensions secretary
OL,7,FHelen Whately said: "Finally the dam
OL,8,Fbreaks and we get to see what Labour
OL,9,Fhave known all along...
OL,11,F"Clearly Keir Starmer feels like
OL,12,Fthat's a price worth paying to make a
OL,13,Fpolitical point. But I don't think
OL,14,Fthose pensioners would agree with him."
OL,16,FGovernment sources said the
OL,17,Fcalculation had emerged from "routine
OL,18,Fpolicy advice" but argued that it
OL,19,Ffailed to take into account the extra
OL,20,Fsupport that was being provided to
OL,21,Fthose who need it.
