OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference in
OL,7,FBrazil, Keir Starmer stressed the
OL,8,Fareas the analysis did not cover -
OL,9,Fincluding an extension to the
OL,10,FHousehold Support Fund, Warm Home
OL,11,FDiscount or the #470 rise to the state
OL,12,Fpension in April.
OL,14,FHowever, the figures do underline the
OL,15,Fway in which the policy shift is
OL,16,Fhitting a number of pensioners who are
OL,17,Fstruggling financially.
