OL,3,CWinter fuel payments cut could drive
OL,4,C100,000 pensioners into poverty
OL,6,FThe Government's argument for means
OL,7,Ftesting Winter Fuel payments was that
OL,8,Fit could not justify paying the
OL,9,Fbenefits to rich pensioners in such
OL,10,Ftricky economic times.
OL,12,FSo they restricted pay outs to only
OL,13,Fthose who claim pension credit.
OL,14,FHowever, the shift has shone a light
OL,15,Fon the fact that only 63% of those who
OL,16,Fqualify for pension credit claim it,
OL,17,Fmeaning plenty of poorer pensioners
OL,18,Fare in line to miss out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
