OL,3,CWinter fuel payments cut could drive
OL,4,C100,000 pensioners into poverty
OL,6,FStarmer argued that the numbers also
OL,7,Fdid not account for the Government's
OL,8,Fdrive to get more people to sign up
OL,9,Ffor pension credit, and in doing so
OL,10,Falso qualify for Winter Fuel Payments
OL,11,Fonce more.
OL,13,FThe actual figure for the number of
OL,14,Fextra pensioners in poverty jumps
OL,15,Fbetween #50,000 and #100,000 for each
OL,16,Fyear up to 2029/30 - because the
OL,17,Fnumbers are rounded up to the closest
OL,18,F#100,000 - so the actual figure is
OL,19,Fsomewhere in between.
